The paper deals with understanding and visualizing the internal representations of CNNs, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for decoding CNN features, which is a technique that falls under the umbrella of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of convolutional layers, which are a common component of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with visualizing CNN features in terms of the image space, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM).
